Class ConfigPropertyCallback

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cyclops.cyclopscore.config.ConfigPropertyCallback

  • public final class ConfigPropertyCallback
extends java.lang.Object
    A helper class to contain callbacks for when the config file has been read so that set values can be updated in the config objects.
